lock text-sm text-gray-800\" data-kid=\"115\">Voltic XI</span>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"font-body font-black text-[#00A550]\" data-kid=\"116\">412</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <button class=\"w-full mt-6 py-4 bg-white/40 rounded-2xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-400 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-200 hover:border-[#FF4F00] hover:text-[#FF4F00] transition-all text-xs\" data-kid=\"117\">View All 124 Teams</button>\n                </div>\n\n                \n                <div class=\"clay-surface bg-white rounded-[40px] p-10 flex flex-col gap-6 h-[270px] justify-center group hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"118\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"119\">\n                        <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-[#00A550]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#00A550] text-2xl shadow-sm border border-[#00A550]/20 group-hover:bg-[#00A550] group-hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"120\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-users\" data-kid=\"121\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-heading text-2xl font-bold\" data-kid=\"122\">Team Control</h3>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"font-body text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium\" data-kid=\"123\">Manage substitutions and track attendance with one tap.</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex -space-x-3\" data-kid=\"124\">\n                        <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=1\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm\" data-kid=\"125\">\n                        <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=2\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm\" data-kid=\"126\">\n                        <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=3\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm\" data-kid=\"127\">\n                        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 border-4 border-white flex items-center justify-center font-heading font-bold text-gray-400 text-xs\" data-kid=\"128\">+5</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"relative min-h-[900px] bg-[#FF4F00] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-24\" data-kid=\"129\">\n        \n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-40 mix-blend-soft-light pointer-events-none\" style=\"background: radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, #ff8c4f 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, #ff4f00 0%, transparent 50%);\" data-kid=\"130\"></div>\n        \n        \n        <video class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-25 mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://images.pexels.com/videos/8516640/abstract-abstraction-animation-anniversary-8516640.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&fit=crop&h=1200&w=630\" data-kid=\"131\">\n            <source src=\"https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/8516640/8516640-hd_1080_1920_30fps.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" data-kid=\"132\">\n        </video>\n        \n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_transparent_0%,_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)_100%)] pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"133\"></div>\n\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center w-full max-w-4xl\" data-kid=\"134\">\n            \n            <div class=\"relative h-[620px] w-full flex items-end justify-center mb-12\" data-kid=\"135\">\n                <div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-center w-full\" data-kid=\"136\">\n                    \n                    <div class=\"w-[440px] h-[100px] bg-white rounded-[50%/50px] relative shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] border-b-[15px] border-gray-100 transform preserve-3d\" id=\"pedestal\" data-kid=\"137\">\n                        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-full border-4 border-white\" data-kid=\"138\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 glossy-overlay rounded-full opacity-30\" data-kid=\"139\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <div class=\"absolute bottom-[50px] w-[260px] h-[520px] bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-[48px] p-3.5 border-[10px] border-[#222] shadow-[0_50px_100px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] z-20 flex flex-col overflow-hidden\" id=\"phone-display\" data-kid=\"140\">\n                        <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-[#F8F8FF] rounded-[32px] p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center\" data-kid=\"141\">\n                            <div class=\"mt-6 mb-8 transform hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 relative\" data-kid=\"142\">\n                                <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-yellow-400/20 blur-3xl rounded-full\" data-kid=\"143\"></div>\n                                <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/openmoji-named-svgs@latest/color/trophy.svg\" class=\"w-36 h-36 drop-shadow-2xl relative z-10\" data-kid=\"144\">\n                            </div>\n                            <h2 class=\"font-heading text-4xl font-black text-[#FF4F00] mb-3 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"145\">VICTORY!</h2>\n                            <p class=\"font-body text-gray-400 font-bold text-[9px] mb-8 uppercase tracking-[0.25em] leading-tight\" data-kid=\"146\">TEAM SCUDERIA ACE</p>\n                            <div class=\"w-full space-y-4\" data-kid=\"147\">\n                                <div class=\"h-6 w-full bg-gray-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden p-0.5 shadow-inner\" data-kid=\"148\">\n                                    <div class=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00A550] to-[#00c860] w-[85%] rounded-full\" data-kid=\"149\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center font-heading font-black text-gray-300 text-[10px]\" data-kid=\"150\">\n                                    <span data-kid=\"151\">LEVEL UP</span>\n                                    <span class=\"text-[#00A550]\" data-kid=\"152\">+1,240 XP</span>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            \n            <button class=\"gummy-pill font-heading px-12 py-6 text-3xl font-black text-[#FF4F00] uppercase tracking-tighter\" id=\"cta-button\" data-kid=\"153\">\n                Download Now\n            </button>\n            <p class=\"font-body text-white/60 mt-6 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"154\">Available on App Store & Play Store</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <footer class=\"bg-gray-900 py-20 px-20 text-white overflow-hidden relative\" data-kid=\"155\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-20\" data-kid=\"156\">\n            <div class=\"col-span-2\" data-kid=\"157\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-8\" data-kid=\"158\">\n                    <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#FF4F00] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg\" data-kid=\"159\">\n                        <i class=\"ti ti-trophy text-white text-xl\" data-kid=\"160\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"font-heading text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"161\">TurfScore<span class=\"text-[#FF4F00]\" data-kid=\"162\">Pro</span></span>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"font-body text-gray-400 text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-sm\" data-kid=\"163\">\n                    Making amateur sports feel like the big leagues. Join 100k+ players today.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n            <div data-kid=\"164\">\n                <h4 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"165\">Product</h4>\n                <ul class=\"space-y-4 font-body text-gray-400 text-lg\" data-kid=\"166\">\n                    <li data-kid=\"167\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"168\">Features</a></li>\n                    <li data-kid=\"169\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"170\">Leagues</a></li>\n                    <li data-kid=\"171\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"172\">Pricing</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div data-kid=\"173\">\n                <h4 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-8\" data-kid=\"174\">Connect</h4>\n                <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"175\">\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#FF4F00] transition-all\" data-kid=\"176\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram text-2xl\" data-kid=\"177\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#FF4F00] transition-all\" data-kid=\"178\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter text-2xl\" data-kid=\"179\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#FF4F00] transition-all\" data-kid=\"180\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-discord text-2xl\" data-kid=\"181\"></i></a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center font-body text-gray-500\" data-kid=\"182\">\n            &copy; 2024 Turf Score Pro. Play hard, score big.\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    \n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"183\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"184\"></script>\n    <script type=\"module\" data-kid=\"185\">\n        import { animate, scroll, spring } from \"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/motion@12/+esm\"\n        import { animate as animeAnimate, createAnimatable } from 'https://esm.sh/animejs@4';\n\n        gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n        // --- ENTRANCE ANIMATIONS (Motion.js) ---\n        animate(\".hero-word\", \n            { scale: [0.5, 1], opacity: [0, 1], y: [50, 0] }, \n            { type: \"spring\", bounce: 0.4, delay: (index) => index * 0.1, visualDuration: 0.6 }\n        );\n\n        animate(\"#hero-cta\", \n            { scale: [0, 1], opacity: [0, 1] }, \n            { type: \"spring\", bounce: 0.6, delay: 0.4, visualDuration: 0.8 }\n        );\n\n        // --- AMBIENT FLOATING (Anime.js) ---\n        document.querySelectorAll('.float-item').forEach(item => {\n            const speed = parseFloat(item.dataset.speed || 1);\n            animeAnimate(item, {\n                translateY: [-15 * speed, 15 * speed],\n                duration: 2500 / speed,\n                direction: 'alternate',\n                loop: true,\n                easing: 'easeInOutQuad'\n            });\n        });\n\n        // --- CARD TILT INTERACTION (Anime.js v4) ---\n        document.querySelectorAll('.tilt-target').forEach(card => {\n            const t = createAnimatable(card, { rotateX: 0, rotateY: 0, scale: 1 });\n            \n            card.addEventListener('pointermove', e => {\n                const r = card.getBoundingClientRect();\n                const x = ((e.clientX - r.left) / r.width - 0.5) * 30;\n                const y = ((e.clientY - r.top) / r.height - 0.5) * -30;\n                t.rotateY(x);\n                t.rotateX(y);\n                t.scale(1.05);\n            });\n\n            card.addEventListener('pointerleave', () => {\n                animeAnimate(card, {\n                    rotateX: 0,\n                    rotateY: 0,\n                    scale: 1,\n                    duration: 800,\n                    easing: 'spring(1, 80, 10, 0)'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n\n        // --- FLAG WIGGLE (Anime.js) ---\n        const flagContainer = document.getElementById('ref-flag-container');\n        if (flagContainer) {\n            flagContainer.addEventListener('pointerenter', () => {\n                animeAnimate(flagContainer, {\n                    rotate: [0, -15, 12, -8, 5, 0],\n                    duration: 600,\n                    easing: 'easeOutQuad'\n                });\n            });\n        }\n\n        // --- CTA GUMMY INTERACTION (Anime.js) ---\n        const btn = document.getElementById('cta-button');\n        if (btn) {\n            btn.addEventListener('pointerdown', () => {\n                animeAnimate(btn, { scale: 0.92, rotateX: 10, duration: 150, easing: 'easeOutQuad' });\n            });\n            btn.addEventListener('pointerup', () => {\n                animeAnimate(btn, { \n                    scale: 1, \n                    rotateX: 0, \n                    duration: 800, \n                    easing: 'spring(1, 80, 10, 0)'\n                });\n            });\n        }\n\n        // --- SCROLL EFFECTS (GSAP & Motion) ---\n        gsap.to(\"#pedestal\", {\n            scrollTrigger: {\n                trigger: \"#pedestal\",\n                start: \"top bottom\",\n                end: \"bottom top\",\n                scrub: 1\n            },\n            rotateY: 45,\n            ease: \"none\"\n        });\n\n        gsap.to(\"#phone-display\", {\n            scrollTrigger: {\n                trigger: \"#phone-display\",\n                start: \"top bottom\",\n                end: \"bottom top\",\n                scrub: 1\n            },\n            translateY: -30,\n            ease: \"none\"\n        });\n\n        // Smooth reveal of features\n        gsap.utils.toArray('.clay-surface, .clay-island').forEach(card => {\n            gsap.from(card, {\n                scrollTrigger: {\n                    trigger: card,\n                    start: \"top 90%\",\n                    toggleActions: \"play none none none\"\n                },\n                y: 40,\n                scale: 0.98,\n                opacity: 0,\n                duration: 1.2,\n                ease: \"expo.out\"\n            });\n        });\n\n        // Phone ambient bob relative to pedestal\n        animeAnimate(\"#phone-display\", {\n            translateY: [-10, 10],\n            duration: 2000,\n            direction: 'alternate',\n            loop: true,\n            easing: 'easeInOutQuad'\n        });\n    </script>\n</div>\n",
